-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Use the “.roll 1d20” command to make a dice roll.
Sends the result through TheBasics' "/it" command

Works with any number.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Multi-lang ! (v0.3.0)
Francais, English, Українська, Русский, Español, 中文, Duits
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage: .roll 2d6 or .roll 3d20.
First value = number of dice.
Second = number of faces.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
